title: Adrian Gross - Jazzology
description:
Adrian Gross

Adrian Gross, a great up and coming jazz guitarist from Montreal on Toronto's Jazz FM 91.1's great show Jazzology.

He will introduce you to his music, his influences and his take on jazz.

This guy will be HUGE so download and have a listen.

For more, check out: www . myspace . com / adriangrossmusic
